# To check out the code and data into a scourge directory
svn co https://svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/scourge/trunk scourge

# To configure it
cd scourge/scourge
autoreconf -i

# To compile it
cd ..
mkdir build
cd build
../scourge/configure --enable-debug
make

# Run
./src/scourge -f

Thanks,
